  "texts": [
    "Nevertheless, persistent challenges and gaps remain, presenting untapped opportunities that governments in the selected EMR countries can leverage to enhance the efficiency of future public health emergency responses.",
    "The methodology and framework developed for this study can be replicated in other settings to assess multi-sectoral collaborations and initiatives to respond to public health crises.",
    "Study findings can inform multi-sectoral initiatives' improvement efforts in the EMR and beyond, with a particular emphasis on fragile settings.FEJ.",
